            array('id' => '23','key' => 'about-section','value' => '{"images":{"image_one":"120ebecf-94c0-4b0b-b0a6-81c671902c77.webp","image_two":"dc4fca5b-eedd-477b-9abb-e24fc567f829.webp","image_three":"1d68dcd7-0f1b-4ca9-a325-47e53e58262c.webp","image_four":"e127b7d8-403f-4f18-86b2-a007b42027fb.webp","image_five":"6273d8be-0c1c-4b76-972c-cb7551f72d18.webp","image_six":"86c5253c-770f-4232-8da4-319d0c473144.webp"},"language":{"en":{"heading":"Making Transactions Effortless: Your Guide to Harnessing the Power of PayLink","details":"PayLink is designed with the needs of entrepreneurs and startups in mind. We understand the importance of keeping costs in check, which is why our solution is not only powerful but also cost-effective. Our aim is to remove the financial barriers that can hinder your growth, ensuring that you can thrive on the global stage without breaking the bank.\\r\\nNavigating the world of international payments can be daunting, but with PayLink, your business will have all the tools it needs to succeed. Our user-friendly platform ensures that you don\\u2019t need to be a tech expert to effectively manage your finances, giving you the time and confidence to focus on what truly matters \\u2013 the growth and success of your business."},"es":{"heading":"Realizar transacciones sin esfuerzo: su gu\\u00eda para aprovechar el poder de PayLink","details":"PayLink est\\u00e1 dise\\u00f1ado teniendo en cuenta las necesidades de los emprendedores y las nuevas empresas. Entendemos la importancia de mantener los costos bajo control, raz\\u00f3n por la cual nuestra soluci\\u00f3n no solo es potente sino tambi\\u00e9n rentable. Nuestro objetivo es eliminar las barreras financieras que pueden obstaculizar su crecimiento, asegurando que pueda prosperar en el escenario global sin arruinarse.\\r\\nNavegar por el mundo de los pagos internacionales puede resultar desalentador, pero con PayLink, su empresa tendr\\u00e1 todas las herramientas que necesita para tener \\u00e9xito. Nuestra plataforma f\\u00e1cil de usar garantiza que no necesita ser un experto en tecnolog\\u00eda para administrar sus finanzas de manera efectiva, brind\\u00e1ndole el tiempo y la confianza para concentrarse en lo que realmente importa: el crecimiento y el \\u00e9xito de su negocio."},"ar":{"heading":"\\u062c\\u0639\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0639\\u0627\\u0645\\u0644\\u0627\\u062a \\u0633\\u0647\\u0644\\u0629: \\u062f\\u0644\\u064a\\u0644\\u0643 \\u0644\\u062a\\u0633\\u062e\\u064a\\u0631 \\u0642\\u0648\\u0629 PayLink","details":"\\u062a\\u0645 \\u062a\\u0635\\u0645\\u064a\\u0645 PayLink \\u0645\\u0639 \\u0623\\u062e\\u0630 \\u0627\\u062d\\u062a\\u064a\\u0627\\u062c\\u0627\\u062a \\u0631\\u0648\\u0627\\u062f \\u0627\\u0644\\u0623\\u0639\\u0645\\u0627\\u0644 \\u0648\\u0627\\u0644\\u0634\\u0631\\u0643\\u0627\\u062a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0646\\u0627\\u0634\\u0626\\u0629 \\u0641\\u064a \\u0627\\u0644\\u0627\\u0639\\u062a\\u0628\\u0627\\u0631. \\u0646\\u062d\\u0646 \\u0646\\u062f\\u0631\\u0643 \\u0623\\u0647\\u0645\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0645\\u0631\\u0627\\u0642\\u0628\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0643\\u0627\\u0644\\u064a\\u0641\\u060c \\u0648\\u0644\\u0647\\u0630\\u0627 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0633\\u0628\\u0628 \\u0641\\u0625\\u0646 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u0644 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0630\\u064a \\u0646\\u0642\\u062f\\u0645\\u0647 \\u0644\\u064a\\u0633 \\u0642\\u0648\\u064a\\u064b\\u0627 \\u0641\\u062d\\u0633\\u0628\\u060c \\u0628\\u0644 \\u0641\\u0639\\u0627\\u0644 \\u0645\\u0646 \\u062d\\u064a\\u062b \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u0643\\u0644\\u0641\\u0629 \\u0623\\u064a\\u0636\\u064b\\u0627. \\u0647\\u062f\\u0641\\u0646\\u0627 \\u0647\\u0648 \\u0625\\u0632\\u0627\\u0644\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062d\\u0648\\u0627\\u062c\\u0632 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0627\\u0644\\u064a\\u0629 \\u0627\\u0644\\u062a\\u064a \\u064a\\u0645\\u0643\\u0646 \\u0623\\u0646 \\u062a\\u0639\\u064a\\u0642 \\u0646\\u0645\\u0648\\u0643\\u060c \\u0645\\u0645\\u0627 \\u064a\\u0636\\u0645\\u0646 \\u0642\\u062f\\u